000100*    THIS COMMENT IS THE FIRST IMAGE IN KP004                     KP0044.2
000200*    ADD  1 TO THE LIST.                                          KP0044.2
000300 PST-INIT-004.                                                    KP0044.2
000400     MOVE "PSEUDO-TEXT/WORD" TO FEATURE.                          KP0044.2
