000700 PST-TEST-004.                                                    KP0044.2
000800     ADD     5 TO WRK-DS-09V00-901.                               KP0044.2
000900     THIS IS NOT REAL COBOL-74 SYNTAX HOWEVER                     KP0044.2
001000             SHOVE +2 TO WRK-DS-09V00-902.                        KP0044.2
