003800 SOURCE-COMPUTER.                                                 RL1024.2
003900     GNU-Linux.                                                   RL1024.2
004000 OBJECT-COMPUTER.                                                 RL1024.2
004100     GNU-Linux.                                                   RL1024.2
004200 INPUT-OUTPUT SECTION.                                            RL1024.2
