004700     "XXXXX021"                                                   RL1024.2
004800             ORGANIZATION IS RELATIVE                             RL1024.2
004900             ACCESS  MODE IS RANDOM                               RL1024.2
005000             RELATIVE KEY RL-FR1-KEY.                             RL1024.2
