007500 01  WRK-CS-09V00-004 PIC S9(09)       USAGE COMP VALUE ZERO.     RL1024.2
007600 01  WRK-CS-09V00-005 PIC S9(09)       USAGE COMP VALUE ZERO.     RL1024.2
