034100     IF P-OR-F EQUAL TO "FAIL*"  PERFORM WRITE-LINE               RL1054.2
034200        PERFORM FAIL-ROUTINE THRU FAIL-ROUTINE-EX                 RL1054.2
034300          ELSE PERFORM BAIL-OUT THRU BAIL-OUT-EX.                 RL1054.2
