032600 FAIL.  MOVE "FAIL*" TO P-OR-F.  ADD 1 TO ERROR-COUNTER.          RL1074.2
032700 DE-LETE.  MOVE "*****" TO P-OR-F.  ADD 1 TO DELETE-COUNTER.      RL1074.2
032800     MOVE "****TEST DELETED****" TO RE-MARK.                      RL1074.2
