034000     MOVE     SPACE TO RE-MARK.                                   RL1074.2
034100 HEAD-ROUTINE.                                                    RL1074.2
034200     MOVE CCVS-H-1  TO DUMMY-RECORD. PERFORM WRITE-LINE 2 TIMES.  RL1074.2
