033700     MOVE "TEST(S) DELETED     " TO ENDER-DESC.                   RL2064.2
033800     MOVE CCVS-E-2 TO DUMMY-RECORD. PERFORM WRITE-LINE.           RL2064.2
033900      IF   INSPECT-COUNTER EQUAL TO ZERO                          RL2064.2
