004700     "XXXXX021"                                                   RL2094.2
004800             ORGANIZATION IS RELATIVE.                            RL2094.2
004900*    ABSENCE OF THE ACCESS CLAUSE IS TREATED AS THOUGH            RL2094.2
005000*     SEQUENTIAL HAD BEEN SPECIFIED.                              RL2094.2
