045000     MOVE   "REL-TEST-002-1-2" TO PAR-NAME.                       RL2104.2
045100     IF      XRECORD-NUMBER (1) > 200                             RL2104.2
045200             IF      RL-VS1R2-F-G-121-124 NOT = 16                RL2104.2
