046400                     MOVE    RL-GROUP          TO COMPUTED-X      RL2104.2
046500                     MOVE   "INVALID RECORD READ" TO RE-MARK      RL2104.2
046600                     PERFORM FAIL                                 RL2104.2
046700                     PERFORM PRINT-DETAIL.                        RL2104.2
