047200 REL-TEST-002-2.                                                  RL2104.2
047300     MOVE   "REL-TEST-002-2" TO PAR-NAME.                         RL2104.2
047400     IF      XRECORD-NUMBER (1) NOT EQUAL TO 500                  RL2104.2
047500             PERFORM FAIL                                         RL2104.2
047600     ELSE                                                         RL2104.2
