002300*                     RELATIVE  I-O DATA FILE (RL-FS1)         *  RL2134.2
002400*             X-22   IMPLEMENTOR-NAME IN ASSIGN TO CLAUSE FOR  *  RL2134.2
002500*                     RELATIVE  I-O DATA FILE (RL-FS2)         *  RL2134.2
002600*             X-55   SYSTEM PRINTER                            *  RL2134.2
